Package: rENM.model
Type: Package
Title: Modeling tools for the rENM Framework
Version: 0.1.0.9000
Authors@R: person(given = "John L.", family = "Schnase",
    email = "rENM.Framework@gmail.com",
    role = c("aut", "cre"),
    comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-7473-3977"))
Description: Provides ecological niche modeling tools for the rENM
    Framework, including occurrence and variable staging, stochastic
    covariance screening, ensemble model construction, and time-series
    assembly across five-year bins using the sdm modeling framework.
